These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, tea
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, thriller
1. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | tea  | juice |
| Movie-Genre       | adventure | thriller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, mystery
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
2. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | mystery |
| Sport      | surfing     | golf  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
