There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, purple
1. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | western  |
| Color   | mauve | purple |

